BUILD:
     make all 
     
     notes : 
     1) build obj for both client and server.


Running :

    1) ntp server (local terminal) :
     ./client_tcp <port>      
     
    2) ntp client (local terminal) :
    ./client_tcp localhost <port> <data>    
     

Testcase:

Run with Virtual box. server and client program run on separated terminal. 
    1) ntp server (local terminal) :
     ./client_tcp 1234      
     
    2) ntp client (local terminal) :
    ./client_tcp localhost 1234 8    

Notes:
      1) Running server/client on two seperated terminal. Then use "localhost" as server address.
